$interpreted: Nolva: This...is probably the handiwork of my monster friend.
Nora: ...Miss Nolva, have you observed any abnormalities?
Nolva: Abnormalities?
Nora: An earthquake, a ray of light, seeing something fall from the sky... stuff like that. Some unknown power has brought us here from Node 08...
Nora: This is the only possible explanation for all this.
NEKO#ΦωΦ: W-w-w-w-wait a second! Nora-chan, do you really believe what this weird girl said?
Nora: The debris here matches Miss Nolva's description.
Nora: She never met us before. No reason for her to deliberately hide information from us. Therefore, the thing that can bring us here all of a sudden...
Nora: ...can only be some form of supernatural power.
PAFF: Nora, do you mean magic...and things like that? That's... way too...

Nora: If we reduce them down to their essence, both science and magic have the power to change the world.
Be it the virtual internet, instant teleportation...
Nora: ...or even your singing and music, they are all the same.

NEKO#ΦωΦ: Errr, I don't understand a word you're saying...
NEKO's gonna make a phone call and ask an expert.
NEKO#ΦωΦ: Meowbot, call Xenon!
Meowbot: Sorry meow~ No signal detected at your current location meow~
NEKO#ΦωΦ: Eh? No signal!? Why?
PAFF: Let me try as well. Tuner-san...
PAFF: Woah!
Nolva: What's the matter!?
Nolva: Nora? Everyone? What's going on...
Nolva: ......Ah!
Nolva: Waverlyde, help me protect everyone...
Nolva: I'll leave it to you...
Nolva: Eh? I didn't fall asleep? ...Waverlyde?
Nora: Look out!
Nolva: Wow, everyone is so amazing...
Nolva: ...Miss NEKO? Are you alright?
NEKO#ΦωΦ: ...My head...it's hurting more and more...
NEKO#ΦωΦ: This, all this...What on earth is going on now!!!
NEKO#ΦωΦ: ...Getting dragged to this creepy place out of nowhere, and now I'm fighting scary monsters...
PAFF: NEKO, are you alright...
PAFF: Waaah!

NEKO#ΦωΦ: Stay away from me, you trouble magnet!
Nothing good ever happens when I'm around you!

NEKO#ΦωΦ: You're just a dumb idol who knows nothing besides singing! That's all you're good for!
Leave me alone!
PAFF: Oh no, NEKO ran out all by herself...
PAFF: I-I...I have to get her back!

Nora: ...The monsters we just encountered, it seems that a lot of them are still wandering around nearby.
If we want to find her, we better hurry.
Nolva: This machine...can detect the monsters? Incredible...
Nora: Scanning is merely one of its basic functions.
Nora: The main function of Unit-01 is to simulate voiceprints, which allows me to talk normally.
Nolva: Oh, so your voice is...
Nora: ...It's not a big deal. Don't worry about it. Let's get going now.
Nora: If it's NEKO, she'll definitely run around and cause a big mess. We'd better find her before she gets into trouble.
PAFF: Nora knows NEKO as well?
Nora: Yes...she's a celebrity, after all.
PAFF: Ah, you know her in that regard...
Nora: ...We better hurry. Neither of us is familiar with this place. Miss Nolva, could you lead the way?
Nolva: M-me?
PAFF: Please... please...
Nolva: ......
Nolva: Alright, let me help. Come on, come with me.
